      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean yeah, i get that it's a \"human experience\" but it feels less like a feeling and more like a fact. like, there is no real difference between me being here or me being gone. it wouldn't change the math for anyone. it would just be... quiet. and maybe that's better than this constant feeling of just being a shadow.",
